📊 Project Report: Trend Analyzer using AI Agents
1. Introduction

The Trend Analyzer project is designed to identify and analyze current trends using AI-powered agents and external data sources. It leverages modern tools such as language models and APIs to gather, process, and interpret trending information efficiently. The system is built using Python and integrates multiple services for intelligent data analysis.

2. Objective

The main objectives of this project are:

To analyze current trends from various online sources
To automate data collection and processing
To generate meaningful insights using AI models
To demonstrate the use of agent-based architectures
3. Technologies Used
Python – Core programming language
Google ADK (Agent Development Kit) – For building AI agents
LiteLLM Model – For natural language processing
Exa API – For search-based data retrieval
Tavily Client – For web search and insights
Firecrawl – For web scraping and crawling
dotenv – For managing environment variables
4. System Architecture

The system uses a multi-agent architecture:

SequentialAgent: Executes tasks step-by-step
LlmAgent: Processes and generates insights using AI
Runner: Manages execution of agents
Session Service: Stores temporary session data

The model used (Meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct) processes user queries and generates responses based on collected data.

5. Working of the System
Environment variables are loaded securely using .env
API keys and base URLs are configured
The LiteLLM model is initialized
Agents are created to handle:
Data collection
Processing
Analysis
External APIs (Exa, Tavily, Firecrawl) fetch real-time data
The system analyzes trends and produces results
6. Features
Real-time trend analysis
Integration with multiple data sources
AI-based insights generation
Modular and scalable architecture
Secure API handling
7. Advantages
Saves time in manual research
Provides accurate and fast insights
Easily extendable with new APIs
Efficient use of AI agents
8. Limitations
Depends on API availability and rate limits
Requires internet connectivity
May produce biased results based on data sources
9. Future Enhancements
Add visualization dashboards
Improve accuracy using advanced models
Integrate more data sources
Deploy as a web application
10. Conclusion

The Trend Analyzer project demonstrates how AI agents and APIs can be combined to create a powerful system for analyzing trends. It highlights the effectiveness of automation and intelligent systems in handling large-scale data and generating useful insights
